<plot>In 1934, MGM held a convention in Chicago, inviting its company distributors from all over the United States to preview the films scheduled for the 1934-1935 exhibition season. After a welcome from studio executive 'Felix E. Feist' (qv), the people in each geographic division are introduced, and the chief of each division says a few words.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?348965</url></doc>
